                    <h3>Free Shipping</h3>
                    <p>You heard it right. DVDEmpire is offering Free Shipping on all orders of $25.00 or more worth of merchandise! Packages will be shipped our Standard Shipping option and the shipping is completely FREE. <br>
                        We ship your order the same day if everything is IN STOCK and you place your order by 3:00PM ET. All Free Shipping packages shipped Standard Shipping will take about 3 - 7 business days to be delivered (Restrictions Apply).</p>
                    <strong>How To Receive Free Shipping:</strong>
                    <hr></hr>
                    <ol>
                        <li>1. Build an order of your favorite DVDs, Blurays, etc. that totals $25.00 or more</li>
                        <li>2. Order must be shipped within the United States (International shipments do not qualify for Free Shipping).</li>
                        <li>3. Select "Standard Shipping" as your shipping method.</li>
                        <li>4. Click the 'Send Order' button at the bottom of the Checkout page.</li>
                        <li>5. That's it! Your Order will be shipped for free!</li>
                    </ol><br>
                    <strong>Restrictions:</strong>
                    <hr>
                    <ul>
                        <li>• Our Free Shipping offer is for Orders shipping within the United States only (NO International Shipments).</li>
                        <li>• Only orders that a merchandise total of $25.00 or more after all discounts have been applied (coupons, bundle discounts, etc) qualify for free shipping.</li>
                        <li>• Eligible Products will have the 'Eligible for free shipping' link below the Stock Status on their Item Page.</li>
                        <li>• Ineligible Products will have the 'Not eligible for free shipping' link below the Stock Status on their Item Page.</li>
                        <li>• Any order containing an Ineligible Product will not ship for Free.</li>
                        <li>• Our Free Shipping offer is for Orders shipping within the United States only (NO International shipments).</li>
                        <li>• Used Products purchased from eSellers are NOT eligible for Free Shipping.</li>
                        <li>• Used products bought from DVD Empire (listed under the seller name: DVD Empire) are eligible toward our Free Shipping offer.</li>
